                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Write a method to compute all permutations of a string whose characters are not necessarily unique. The list of permutations should not have duplicates. **Example:** ``` Input: S = \"qqe\" Output: [\"eqq\",\"qeq\",\"qqe\"] ``` **Note:** All permutations of the string should be in lexicographic order. The length of the string won't exceed 8."
                        }
                    ]
